== Описание ==

The '''TechDraw ExtensionPositionSectionView''' tool orthogonally aligns a section view with its source view. You can select [[#Usage_view_selection|a section view]] or ({{Version|1.0}}) select [[#Usage_edge_vertex_selection|an edge and a vertex]].

==Usage - view selection==

[[Image:TechDraw_ExtensionPositionSectionViewExample.png|400px]]
{{Caption|On the right the aligned section view}}

# Select a section view.
# There are several ways to invoke the tool:
#* Press the {{Button|[[Image:TechDraw_ExtensionPositionSectionView.svg|16px]] [[TechDraw_ExtensionPositionSectionView|Position Section View]]}} button.
#* Select the {{MenuCommand|TechDraw → Extensions: Attributes/Modifications → [[Image:TechDraw_ExtensionPositionSectionView.svg|16px]] Position Section View}} option from the menu.
# The section view is aligned with its source view.

==Usage - edge and vertex selection==

[[Image:TechDraw_ExtensionPositionSectionViewExample2.png|400px]]
{{Caption|On the right the aligned section view}}

# Select an edge (1) in a section view. The edge should match the direction of the projection.
# Select the corresponding vertex (2) in the source view.
# There are several ways to invoke the tool:
#* Press the {{Button|[[Image:TechDraw_ExtensionPositionSectionView.svg|16px]] [[TechDraw_ExtensionPositionSectionView|Position Section View]]}} button.
#* Select the {{MenuCommand|TechDraw → Extensions: Attributes/Modifications → [[Image:TechDraw_ExtensionPositionSectionView.svg|16px]] Position Section View}} option from the menu.
# The section view is aligned with its source view.


